parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to a lack of protection in the event of an accident, increasing the risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: Airbag light comes on and flashes
no horn function.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering system can cause loss of control, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Vehicle veers to the left when driving over rough roads or potholes
steering becomes difficult to control
steering wheel moves suddenly and erratically
power-steering fluid leaks out.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The lack of stability and control can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially when driving on uneven surfaces.
symptoms: Vehicle veers to the left when driving over rough roads or potholes
steering becomes difficult to control

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The presence of multiple defects can lead to a decrease in vehicle safety and performance, potentially causing accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Multiple defects
including those related to the airbag system
steering system
and vehicle stability.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the passenger airbag sensor can lead to the airbag not deploying in the event of a crash, potentially causing serious injury or death to the passenger.
symptoms: The airbag light is illuminated on the dashboard
the passenger airbag sensor is faulty
the airbag may not deploy in the event of a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag system can cause the airbag to deploy unexpectedly or not deploy at all in the event of a crash, potentially causing serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag light is illuminated on the dashboard
the airbag deploys unexpectedly
the airbag does not deploy in the event of a crash
the seatbelt light is illuminated on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag cable can cause the airbag to malfunction, potentially leading to serious injury or death in the event of a crash.
symptoms: The airbag light is illuminated on the dashboard
the airbag cable needs to be replaced
the airbag may not deploy in the event of a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden detachment of the rear overhead console can cause distraction, injury, or even fatalities, especially if it falls on occupants, including children, while driving.
symptoms: The rear overhead console falls or detaches from the roof
making a knocking or rattling noise
often accompanied by broken or melted plastic clips or brackets.
